{
  "stem": "20218.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But before they took us out of that hall, they made a selection like-- I remember like today.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "My father came down from the train, my mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They could hardly walk from hunger and from exhaustion.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Anyway, the-- they, they, they put a finger on my father to go one way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Me and my mother, they put on the other side.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I never saw my father again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He was looking out and the last words he said before we went from the train, he said, stay close to your mother.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And they took him away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They took him away with other people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Me and my mother came to a big, big hall.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They asked us to take everything off, just to be naked, and put it on the floor.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That time, somebody told us-- I don't remember, a woman or a man.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They took women on one side, men on the other, that I shouldn't say that I am my mother's daughter because they will push-- put me someplace else.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They would-- they would never let me stay with my mother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "So my mother took her maiden name, but we still were together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "From there, they took us to another room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "They shaved our heads bare.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Matter of fact, I didn't recognize my own mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They took us again to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I mean, that-- we were in Auschwitz, but the outskirts-- in, in the camp, there was a camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] They segregated us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Some of them were younger.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Some of them were older.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "They put us on the-- on the floor, a lot of people in one room.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "When we had to go to the bathroom, there were bathrooms outside, like outhouses.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
